description: Join David as he wins an unlikely fight with Goliath, the giant. This classic Old Testament story teaches children that anything is possible with God on your side. Between the book’s captivating illustrations and easy-to-read text, young readers will find it simple to understand this important lesson. Published by MangoSense.
